{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"4098","text":"Students in the public schools are thus to be taught at an early age that  evolution is a fact  and as time goes by they will gradually learn that evolution means naturalism","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:23"},{"nodeID":"4099","text":"The student who thinks that 2 and 2 make 5 or that water is not made up of hydrogen and oxygen or that the theory of evolution is not true is not expressing a minority viewpoint. He or she is ignorant and the job of education is to cure that ignorance and to replace it with knowledge.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:23"},{"nodeID":"4100","text":"The former is then classified as knowledge","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:23"},{"nodeID":"4101","text":"Belief cannot be taught as knowledge","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:23"},{"nodeID":"4102","text":"Theism is never passed as knowledge it is only valid for the believer","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:23"},{"nodeID":"4103","text":"If something is labelled as knowledge it becomes a fact that must be taught in the public schools","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4104","text":"It labels naturalism as a science","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4105","text":"Science is knowledge","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4106","text":"The distinction is of critical importance because only knowledge can be objectively valid for everyone; belief is valid only for the believer and should never be passed off as knowledge.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4107","text":"the latter as mere belief","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4108","text":"it labels naturalism as science and theism as religion","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4109","text":"Religion is belief","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24"},{"nodeID":"4110","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24","scheme":"Analogy","schemeID":"1"},{"nodeID":"4111","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:24","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"},{"nodeID":"4112","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:25","scheme":"VerbalClassification","schemeID":"31"},{"nodeID":"4113","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:25","scheme":"VerbalClassification","schemeID":"31"},{"nodeID":"4114","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:31:25","scheme":"VerbalClassification","schemeID":"31"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"3862","fromID":"4099","toID":"4110","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3863","fromID":"4110","toID":"4098","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3864","fromID":"4100","toID":"4111","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3865","fromID":"4101","toID":"4111","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3866","fromID":"4102","toID":"4111","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3867","fromID":"4103","toID":"4111","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3868","fromID":"4111","toID":"4098","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3869","fromID":"4104","toID":"4112","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3870","fromID":"4105","toID":"4112","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3871","fromID":"4112","toID":"4100","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3872","fromID":"4106","toID":"4113","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3873","fromID":"4107","toID":"4113","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3874","fromID":"4113","toID":"4102","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3875","fromID":"4108","toID":"4114","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3876","fromID":"4109","toID":"4114","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3877","fromID":"4114","toID":"4107","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}